{"tid":882563,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"做廢青做到啲街坊都認得自己 是否可悲","createTime":"2018-10-30T08:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T06:41:39.000Z","uid":41841,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b01959b9ba990d3c5ff65c2a2c0ade1f47ad797d","tid":882563,"uid":41841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"有次落樓下食飯 個看更同我講：「X生！又食下午茶呀？」<br />\n<br />\n事關我每日訓到兩三點起身 刷完個牙就會落樓下餐廳食我第一餐  每次食半個零鐘就會返返屋企打機<br />\n<br />\n可能因為咁 個看更已經估到 <br />\n<br />\n我尷尷尬尬咁答左句：「哈哈.....係呀！」<br />\n<br />\n又有一次去到間餐廳 食完之後坐左喺到諗住睇陣手機先走<br />\n<br />\n點知個伙記行左埋黎嗒嗲：「咦！細佬，你唔洗返工既咩？」<br />\n<br />\n我情急之下講左個大話：「唔係呀...我返夜！」<br />\n<br />\n果次之後先發現 原來我已經做左咁耐廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f656348cdfbec0513510263a0a4d159df4fe0a","tid":882563,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"你點生活？"},{"pid":"4bd0efbbc1b0624587ce56c97fd549802682d138","tid":882563,"uid":88503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:18:46.000Z","msg":"如果只係慢慢搣緊之前儲落嘅錢<br />\n廢又何妨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f674e4f6257d498ef2f331c81cba54e898d7c9","tid":882563,"uid":156121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"二三十歲享受退休生活<br />\n做生做死做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e016136550afa9a2dd6d977f06f7d7f83b9dba3","tid":882563,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f674e4f6257d498ef2f331c81cba54e898d7c9","tid":882563,"uid":156121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"二三十歲享受退休生活<br />\n做生做死做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"香港人=唔返工人生冇意義了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好7天工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606007b9d45f9a0c82c238afc8da8ba11a7f5c41","tid":882563,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"佢鬼知你係咪廢青<br />\n你都講返夜<br />\n不如話你自己心虛"},{"pid":"0c2944eeec4f01ee8224b7923b07ccf2f371ee4b","tid":882563,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"廢青先係人生贏家<br />\n你應該自豪先岩"}]}